Egg group - HUMAN-LIKE

Ignoring their injuries, groups attack by sinking the blades that cover their bodies into their prey. If battling dulls them, it sharpens them on stones by the river.
This pitiless Pok√©mon commands a group of Pawniard to hound prey into immobility. It battles to become the boss, but will be driven from the group if it loses.
